    "description": "<strong>Bricks of Camels</strong> brings creative minds together in a competitive arena where you control animal characters to build structures using brick-like pieces. Whether you’re a camel, a donkey, or a GOAT, each animal has its unique style and personality, making your building experience as delightful as it is challenging!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHOOSE YOUR CHARACTER</h2>Pick from a variety of animal characters and let your creativity run wild.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/25e327cc5abbf639f3291e36d54665bf.poster.avif?t=1726952430\" width=596 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/25e327cc5abbf639f3291e36d54665bf.webm?t=1726952430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/25e327cc5abbf639f3291e36d54665bf.mp4?t=1726952430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RACE AGAINST TIME</h2>At the start of each game, a common word is given, and you have only 5 minutes to build your best interpretation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/c18dfbffcad5460f1e8f755f5536c4c4.poster.avif?t=1726952430\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/c18dfbffcad5460f1e8f755f5536c4c4.webm?t=1726952430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/c18dfbffcad5460f1e8f755f5536c4c4.mp4?t=1726952430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VOTE</h2>Once time’s up, players vote on each other’s creations to determine the winner.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/93e74530989f78c538dc3a2dd1b51fad.poster.avif?t=1726952430\" width=596 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/93e74530989f78c538dc3a2dd1b51fad.webm?t=1726952430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/93e74530989f78c538dc3a2dd1b51fad.mp4?t=1726952430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WIN AND CONQUER</h2>The player with the most votes wins the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/49879a15e7cd9c6a1e701ed3c609d0b4.poster.avif?t=1726952430\" width=596 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/49879a15e7cd9c6a1e701ed3c609d0b4.webm?t=1726952430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/49879a15e7cd9c6a1e701ed3c609d0b4.mp4?t=1726952430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
